{
  "name": "Hidden Shadow Snake Burial",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Synthetic%20Human.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The user burrows their arms underground and extends their limbs to grab an opponent by their ankles, dragging them into the ground, and burying them with only their head being exposed. The target must succeed a Dexterity Saving Throw, being restrained and unable to make HS on a failure. If the target is unaware of your presence, they make their save at disadvantage. Creatures who are restrained by this jutsu can make a Strength Saving Throw as an action on their turn to end the effect of this jutsu. This jutsu ignores cover.</p>",
